name: coreutils

variants.name: gprefix
variants.description: prefix commands with 'g', to avoid conflicts with OS utilities

description:
The GNU Core Utilities are the basic file, shell and text manipulation
utilities of the GNU operating system. These are the core utilities
which are expected to exist on every operating system.

dependent_to.name: zziplib
dependent_to.description:
The zziplib provides read access to zipped files in a zip-archive, using
compression based solely on free algorithms provided by zlib. It also
provides a functionality to overlay the archive filesystem with the
filesystem of the operating system environment.

dependent_to.name: sloccount
dependent_to.description:
SLOCCount is a set of tools for counting physical Source Lines of Code
(SLOC) in a large number of languages of a potentially large set of
programs.
